{"tid":1297903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《深切反省》唔好BLOCK人！！","createTime":"2019-07-08T17:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T03:31:27.000Z","uid":8230,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cfbc07b033015e033cce4ae0f7c4b0987f4fb76a","tid":1297903,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"見到經過今晚之後好多人話要Block哂今晚玩膠嘅人或者趁亂分化嘅人，我想講<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好block</span>！Block左佢，只會任由fake news，膠post 橫行，你連啲Post都見唔到仲點指正返其他人？！<br />\n<br />\n想同各連登巴絲講，我地要清楚今時今日呢個平台嘅影響力。當我地出一個post已經可以收民建聯晚宴皮嘅時候，我哋講嘅嘢、出嘅post都好有影響力！非常時期我地更加應該用呢一份影響力早啲近有建設性嘅行動。<br />\n利申：我本人都有玩膠開膠post，起呢度再次道歉，精神緊繃左好多日，一見到膠post就放鬆左，冇諗過後果，真係好對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n致各位同路人，經過今次，我地會好好反省，絕對唔會比同類型嘅野再發生。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭現場消息除左睇連登，fb外，仲有各telegram channel可以得到即時消息。<br />\n如scoot scout<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/scottscout\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fscottscout&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=553bec29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/scottscout</a><br />\n612 reminder<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/reminder612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Freminder612&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl7mzrwQ2WUj2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=94dea7e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/reminder612</a>"},{"pid":"54f6bf9e56c7f1407ac78f8baf787aeb8884d7a4","tid":1297903,"uid":8230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:08:39.000Z","msg":"堆！雖然block人係眼不見為淨，不過其他人都會繼續見到，不治本！"},{"pid":"ecfd2d5a0c31d1a9d14fe214445aff09b496481c","tid":1297903,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:09:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><del>堆</del><span style=\"color: red;\">推</span>！雖然block人係眼不見為淨，不過其他人都會繼續見到，不治本！</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ceb16b13b8a873f8f6cb02fd16d3f2f840c692c0","tid":1297903,"uid":9736,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:09:26